title: Oasys Enters Strategic Collaboration With Payment Solution Provider Singularity
description: Singapore-based gaming blockchain Oasys announced a strategic partnership with Singularity, a cross-chain payment solution provider to introduce seamless payments within the Oasys ecosystem. The partnership aims to improve the user experience on the platform offering gamers “unparalleled convenience, ease of use and utility” within the platform.
